<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Trifolium variegatum </i>and other clovers likely coevolved with fire in cismontane California. However, the relative influence and optimal frequency of such fires are speculative (Wills 2006).</div>
